The decision comes following legal consultations in the wake of a Democratic Alliance (DA) court challenge over the suspensions last week. JOHANNESBURG - JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng MEC for CoGTA Lebogang Maile has rescinded the suspensions of former Speaker of the City of Johannesburg Vasco Da Gama and current Speaker of the City of Tshwane Katlego Mathebe. The decision comes following legal consultations in the wake of a Democratic Alliance (DA) court challenge over the suspensions last week. More to follow.